-- EADS’s Cassidian Unit Wants to Build European Drone, FAZ Reports
-- B y   A n n e t t e   W e i s b a c h
-- 2012-07-10T17:20:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-10/eads-s-cassidian-unit-wants-to-build-european-drone-faz-reports.html
European Aeronautic, Defence & Space
Co.’s Cassidian defense unit wants to build a joint European
drone and anticipates an agreement as soon as the end of this
year or the beginning of 2013, Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung
reported, citing Stefan Zoller, chief operating officer of
Cassidian.  Development of the drone will be led by France and  Germany ,
FAZ said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Annette Weisbach in Frankfurt at 
